data.description: Serene and peaceful are two words that describe this home perfectly. A blend of neutral tones throughout bring calming closure to the end of a long day. This well cared for Cape style home located in the beautiful town of Sandwich, Massachusetts offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, and a home office to give you plenty of space to relax and entertain. Deeded access to nearby 138 acre Lawrence Pond, a wonderful spot for bass fishing, paddleboarding, & kayaking, gives you plenty of ways to spend a summer's day! Walk into a warm and inviting living room with wood floors, fireplace, and lots of natural light. Whether you are sitting down for dinner or grabbing a bite on the go, this eat-in kitchen with kitchen island give you options!  A three season breezeway is great for shaking off beach sand or making that perfect book nook you've always wanted. The main bedroom is conveniently set on the first floor for the option of one floor living. Garage, Firepit and .45 acres of land. Ready to move in?
